  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc7\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0baa\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b92\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Adjournment of the case against Senior Deputy Inspector General of Police Deshabandhu",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The report of the investigation regarding Senior Deputy Inspector General of Police Deshabandhu Tennakone has been handed over to the Attorney General for alleged dereliction of duty during the outrageous attacks by government supporters on Maina Ko Kama and Kota Ko Kama.",
        "Today (20) informed Fort Justice Dilina Kamage that they have handed over the report of the investigation done so far to the Attorney General.",
        "The cases related to the outrageous attacks on Maina Ko Kama, Kota Ko Kama by government supporters came up for hearing today in the presence of Fort Justice Dilina Gamage. Meanwhile, the CIT informed the judge.",
        "When the case came up for hearing today, the CIT presented one person as the 36th suspect in the case.",
        "The suspect himself was accused of organizing a pro-Mahinda Rajapaksa rally at Alari House, where he eventually incited the crowd to move to Kota Goma and Maina Go Goma.",
        "Justice Dilina Gamage inquired from the CIT about Senior Deputy Inspector General of Police Deshabandhu Tennakone in response to the request made by the President's lawyer Maithiri Gunaratne who appeared in the forum on behalf of the affected parties.",
        "At the same time, the CID replied that the investigation report on him has been handed over to the Attorney General. In this case, the said case was adjourned till the coming 3rd of August."
      ],
